  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Pescosta family guarantee you a warm welcome to Hotel Sassongher, where their love for South Tyrolean and Ladino culture can be seen throughout. The hotel is synonymous with luxury, peace and relaxation, and it is situated above the village with a splendid back drop of the Sassongher Mountain. Just 4 minutes’ walk (400m) to the village centre, the hotel also provides a free shuttle service.</p>]]></description>
